1123.name: CuAl8Ni2 Tig
1123.Applications: Joint welds or building up of aluminum bronze. Cladding components undergoing metal to metal wear under high pressure. Especially suited for marine environments. The addition of nickel improves corrosion resistance in heat and rough seawater.
1123.Suitable_For: This filler metal with increased strenght and corrosion properties is verry wel suited for Ship propellers, shipbuilding, pump building, shafts, guide grooves etc. W.Nrs: 2.0916,2.0920, 2.0928, 2.0932, 2.0936, 2.0940, 2.0960, 2.0962, 2.0966, 2.0970, 2.0978, 2.0980.
